<p begin="325000000t" end="341700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">豈有此理</p>
<p begin="350000000t" end="390400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">(第十一集 下集決戰)</p>
<p begin="552500000t" end="589600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">在糾纏的業障盡頭眺望</p>
<p begin="589600000t" end="613400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">就連身後也充滿了敵人</p>
<p begin="613400000t" end="627100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">驕傲自大且蠢蠢欲動的</p>
<p begin="627100000t" end="642900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">數以千計的生物們</p>
<p begin="642900000t" end="653700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">dive for alive</p>
<p begin="653790000t" end="665100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">climb for life</p>
<p begin="665100000t" end="690400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">無人生還的混沌狀態</p>
<p begin="690400000t" end="733300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">那就當成我的舞臺吧</p>
<p begin="733300000t" end="747500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">結束了嗎</p>
<p begin="747500000t" end="768300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">可是我還沒有完</p>
<p begin="768300000t" end="797100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">就算你沒看到致命的絲</p>
<p begin="797100000t" end="848400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">只要落網就會被我吃掉</p>
<p begin="848400000t" end="874100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">deeper…inside</p>
<p begin="893300000t" end="915800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">spider pride 又在這個胸膛裡</p>
<p begin="915800000t" end="940000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">刻下殘酷的一痕</p>
<p begin="940000000t" end="961700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">找到最佳解法依然不夠</p>
<p begin="961700000t" end="985900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">必須拼湊被撕裂的生命</p>
<p begin="985900000t" end="1010000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">拚死拚活地思考</p>
<p begin="1010000000t" end="1032500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">你死我活地戰鬥</p>
<p begin="1032500000t" end="1055400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">所謂的真實 feel a bit cold</p>
<p begin="1055400000t" end="1082900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">那就活下去 spider way</p>
<p begin="1147500000t" end="1174200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">那就活下去 spider way</p>
<p begin="1186300000t" end="1196300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">走著瞧吧</p>
<p begin="1196300000t" end="1251300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">(轉生成蜘蛛又怎樣！)</p>
<p begin="1485000000t" end="1497500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">菲</p>
<p begin="1507500000t" end="1520000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">真是的</p>
<p begin="1520000000t" end="1532500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">抱歉…</p>
<p begin="1558800000t" end="1592100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">你退學後已經過了一個多月了吧</p>
<p begin="1592100000t" end="1611700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">是啊</p>
<p begin="1611700000t" end="1653400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">你哥哥的事情</p>
<p begin="1669600000t" end="1732500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">你哥哥們給了魔族軍團沉重的打擊</p>
<p begin="1744600000t" end="1782100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">哈林斯不是也快要回國了嗎</p>
<p begin="1782100000t" end="1812500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">他是勇士隊裡唯一存活下來的人</p>
<p begin="1812500000t" end="1858300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">你哥哥發生了什麼事</p>
<p begin="1858300000t" end="1883300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">他一定會告訴你的</p>
<p begin="1883300000t" end="1923700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">畢竟你身為勇士</p>
<p begin="1929600000t" end="1955000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">勇士啊…</p>
<p begin="1955000000t" end="1973800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">你怎麼了</p>
<p begin="1973800000t" end="2016300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">接替尤利烏斯皇兄的位子</p>
<p begin="2016300000t" end="2066300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">和以前不同</p>
<p begin="2066300000t" end="2117600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">不過悠莉被任命為聖女</p>
<p begin="2142900000t" end="2153700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">我說啊</p>
<p begin="2162100000t" end="2180400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">你和我締結契約吧</p>
<p begin="2180400000t" end="2190800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">咦</p>
<p begin="2190800000t" end="2210000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">咦什麼咦啊</p>
<p begin="2210000000t" end="2241700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">隨時隨地都能召喚我</p>
<p begin="2282500000t" end="2317500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">可是我想和菲平起平坐</p>
<p begin="2317500000t" end="2362900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">而且締結契約後</p>
<p begin="2362900000t" end="2379600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">這樣也沒關係嗎</p>
<p begin="2379600000t" end="2412900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">如果不是緊急情況 你也不會做吧</p>
<p begin="2412900000t" end="2439200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">是這樣沒錯啦</p>
<p begin="2439200000t" end="2483000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">修遇到危險的時候</p>
<p begin="2483000000t" end="2527900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">你看 這樣子你的不安</p>
<p begin="2540000000t" end="2548300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">謝謝妳</p>
<p begin="2548300000t" end="2582500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">不過要怎麼締結契約呢</p>
<p begin="2608800000t" end="2630100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">菲 手伸出來</p>
<p begin="2637100000t" end="2650000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">這樣嗎</p>
<p begin="2787900000t" end="2820800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">好了 這樣就結下契約了</p>
<p begin="2820800000t" end="2844600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">這麼快就結束了</p>
<p begin="2844600000t" end="2870900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">原來這麼簡單就能辦到啊</p>
<p begin="2870900000t" end="2918300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">締結契約很簡單</p>
<p begin="2918300000t" end="2941200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">不會吧</p>
<p begin="2941300000t" end="2953800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">菲</p>
<p begin="2953800000t" end="2974600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">這…這是什麼</p>
<p begin="3035000000t" end="3062500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">菲…菲</p>
<p begin="3084200000t" end="3097100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">(進化中)</p>
<p begin="3097100000t" end="3112100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">進化</p>
<p begin="3128300000t" end="3147900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">心情好差啊</p>
<p begin="3147900000t" end="3176700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">讓我這麼煩躁的原因…</p>
<p begin="3176700000t" end="3189600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">(禁忌等級十)</p>
<p begin="3189600000t" end="3212100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">禁忌</p>
<p begin="3212100000t" end="3264200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">對住在這個世界的人來說</p>
<p begin="3264200000t" end="3280900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">知道這件事後</p>
<p begin="3290800000t" end="3352500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">在禁忌提升到等級十的同時</p>
<p begin="3352500000t" end="3372500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">這個世界的起源</p>
<p begin="3372500000t" end="3389200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">過去發生的事情</p>
<p begin="3389200000t" end="3416700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">技能和能力值的秘密</p>
<p begin="3416700000t" end="3469200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">老實說</p>
<p begin="3469200000t" end="3523800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">情報負責人正在慢慢整理</p>
<p begin="3523800000t" end="3570100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">只有一件事可以肯定</p>
<p begin="3570100000t" end="3584600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">那就是…</p>
<p begin="3584600000t" end="3633400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">這個世界再這樣下去注定會滅亡</p>
<p begin="3680400000t" end="3721200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">既然我知道了這件事</p>
<p begin="3721300000t" end="3735500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">必須想想辦法</p>
<p begin="3735500000t" end="3750800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">沒錯…</p>
<p begin="3750800000t" end="3782100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">我才不要和毀滅的世界同歸於盡</p>
<p begin="3782100000t" end="3810400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">不能再吃美味的食物真討厭</p>
<p begin="3818300000t" end="3860800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">既然如此只能增進技能</p>
<p begin="3860800000t" end="3911600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">就算變強了</p>
<p begin="3911700000t" end="3940000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">連管理員都辦不到唷</p>
<p begin="3940000000t" end="3953800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">不知道</p>
<p begin="3953800000t" end="3991700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">但是我們現在能做的事情</p>
<p begin="3991700000t" end="4038800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">萬一發生什麼事</p>
<p begin="4038800000t" end="4050100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">沒錯</p>
<p begin="4050100000t" end="4083800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">想要在這個世界打倒敵人</p>
<p begin="4083800000t" end="4117100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">所以接下來必須打倒的…</p>
<p begin="4134200000t" end="4154200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">是地龍亞拉巴</p>
<p begin="4195400000t" end="4213300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">妳們不准害怕</p>
<p begin="4213300000t" end="4239600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">居然要挑戰那種怪物 妳有病嗎</p>
<p begin="4239600000t" end="4253800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">對啊…</p>
<p begin="4253800000t" end="4273800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">這群笨蛋</p>
<p begin="4280400000t" end="4297900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">妳做什麼啊</p>
<p begin="4318300000t" end="4358700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">妳們以為我是想打才打的嗎</p>
<p begin="4358800000t" end="4378400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">這…這是什麼意思</p>
<p begin="4378400000t" end="4403700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">妳們打算視而不見到什麼時候</p>
<p begin="4403800000t" end="4439200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">難道妳們都不想克服心理創傷嗎</p>
<p begin="4439200000t" end="4464600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">要是能克服我們也想克服啊</p>
<p begin="4464600000t" end="4494600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">就是因為無法輕易克服</p>
<p begin="4494600000t" end="4502900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">對吧</p>
<p begin="4502900000t" end="4513300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">對啊</p>
<p begin="4529200000t" end="4557100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">夠了 妳們這些分身給我聽好</p>
<p begin="4557100000t" end="4590900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">如果連自己的心理創傷都克服不了</p>
<p begin="4590900000t" end="4642900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">我們要怎麼解救這個世界的危機啊</p>
<p begin="4687500000t" end="4709200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">妳們總算明白了啊</p>
<p begin="4709200000t" end="4741300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">那該做的事就決定了</p>
<p begin="4741300000t" end="4768800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">打倒亞拉巴吧</p>
<p begin="4783300000t" end="4812500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">既然決定好了就去偵查敵情</p>
<p begin="4827900000t" end="4845400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">不准給我害怕</p>
<p begin="4845400000t" end="4859600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">(轉移)</p>
<p begin="4859600000t" end="4881700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">我來到下層了</p>
<p begin="4942100000t" end="4955000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">什麼</p>
<p begin="4955000000t" end="4974600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">不是亞拉巴</p>
<p begin="4987500000t" end="5015400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">好大隻</p>
<p begin="5015400000t" end="5063300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">(艾爾羅霸王蛇 等級25)</p>
<p begin="5063300000t" end="5096200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">要是對上這種傢伙一定會死</p>
<p begin="5096300000t" end="5111700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">請原諒我</p>
<p begin="5210800000t" end="5269100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">下層還有超乎我想像的怪物存在啊</p>
<p begin="5269200000t" end="5301300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">亞拉巴的偵查只能延期了啊</p>
<p begin="5332900000t" end="5356700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">什麼…剛剛那是什麼</p>
<p begin="5356700000t" end="5380000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">從蛇離開的方向…</p>
<p begin="5404200000t" end="5419600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">(望遠)</p>
<p begin="5598800000t" end="5621300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">是重力的魔法</p>
<p begin="5796700000t" end="5837500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">現在開始已經不是戰鬥了</p>
