<p begin="12650000000t" end="12675000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">謝謝大家</p>
<p begin="12697500000t" end="12738300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">看啊 蜜蜂簡直就像垃圾</p>
<p begin="12769600000t" end="12795000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">好像出現了新的蜜蜂</p>
<p begin="12795000000t" end="12840000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">(將軍巨蜂怪 等級四)</p>
<p begin="12917100000t" end="12944200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">(外道魔法幻夢)</p>
<p begin="12944200000t" end="12959600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">開玩笑的</p>
<p begin="12971700000t" end="12995000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">蜂群 也就是說…</p>
<p begin="13009200000t" end="13039600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">那就是蜂巢嗎 好大啊</p>
<p begin="13085400000t" end="13107900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">抱歉打擾你們保護它</p>
<p begin="13107900000t" end="13139200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">因為太麻煩了</p>
<p begin="13161700000t" end="13178800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">接招吧</p>
<p begin="13178800000t" end="13208800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">暗黑槍</p>
<p begin="13326300000t" end="13355100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">經驗值達到一定的目標</p>
<p begin="13365400000t" end="13384600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">安全著陸</p>
<p begin="13432500000t" end="13455400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">總算結束了</p>
<p begin="13455400000t" end="13489600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">本來以為有蜂蜜 竟然沒有</p>
<p begin="13499600000t" end="13516700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">真沒用</p>
<p begin="13524200000t" end="13568800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">好了 去擬定和亞拉巴作戰的計畫</p>
<p begin="13589200000t" end="13621700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">很好 已經準備就緒</p>
<p begin="13621700000t" end="13660500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">還用剩下的技能點數換取了新技能</p>
<p begin="13660500000t" end="13693700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">(怠惰)</p>
<p begin="13693800000t" end="13719200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">能做的事情我全都做了</p>
<p begin="13802100000t" end="13813400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">來了嗎</p>
<p begin="13839200000t" end="13854200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">太好了</p>
<p begin="13854200000t" end="13883400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">當時感受到的恐懼是正確的</p>
<p begin="13890800000t" end="13913700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">(地龍亞拉巴 等級32)</p>
<p begin="13913800000t" end="13935500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">我很害怕</p>
<p begin="13935500000t" end="13957900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">但是卻很高興</p>
<p begin="13957900000t" end="14013700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">你的偵查這麼厲害</p>
<p begin="14022100000t" end="14058800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">你注意到之後</p>
<p begin="14058800000t" end="14075100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">就放我走了吧</p>
<p begin="14089200000t" end="14130000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">我會讓你…後悔自己的高傲</p>
<p begin="14148800000t" end="14173400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">(死神蜘蛛 等級26 沒有名字)</p>
<p begin="14173400000t" end="14200000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">(轉生成蜘蛛又怎樣！)</p>
<p begin="14200000000t" end="14224600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">(敬請期待)</p>
